txt.en: 'Follow me to the gate. From there you must ride!'
'Mount up and defeat the forces ahead. Drive back everyone!'
'The town will not withstand another attack. Grimbold claims you are our last hope!'
'Three cheers for Radwig, warrior and Thane!'
'We were worried you did not survive the assault on the Mead Hall, Thane Radwig!'
'You are as great a warrior as your father, it would seem!'
